<plot>The film "Eternally aliens" is a 24 min. portrait of immigrant youth in two European countries, France and Norway, where violence and illegal activity have become a part of everyday life, and where the search for identity can quickly take a dangerous turn. We participate in a world full of joy, hate, love and racism.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?182956</url></doc>
